Welcome
-------

Although ZeroMQ has a simple API, the internals are quite complex. This project
aims to demystify the internal structure of ZeroMQ. It should be very helpful
for anyone who wants to start contributing to ZeroMQ.


Resources
---------

ZeroMQ Website: http://www.zeromq.org/
Git repository: http://github.com/zeromq/zeromq2

DIA UML editor website: http://live.gnome.org/Dia


